{
  "stem": "17301.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we got back to Prague, there was another we didn't know where to go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So again, we seeked out a-- a Red Cross kitchen to see whether we can get some food, which we did.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They showed us where it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- they told us there is another school that was converted into, you know, for sleeping, a little hotel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's where we-- you know, they had cots, you know, one after-- you know, open, naturally, open space with cots.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's where we settled down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But my sister and my mother were not feeling well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I said to one of the ladies that was in charge, I says, you know, my sister's not feeling good and my mother doesn't either.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So she told us to go to the nearest hospital, which was not too far.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We went to the near-- it wasn't-- it was not-- yeah, it was a-- set up for a hospital.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We went to the nearest place, and they checked my sister and checked my mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they said, yes, they have to be hospitalized because they were really very, very sick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they put them in a hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I stayed behind in this school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I lived there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I visited them, naturally, every day, practically every-- you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was there all day with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then my sister one day said to me, I'm going to die if-- if I don't go home.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I have to go back home to my hometown.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I says, I really don't want to.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "She says, well, I have to, because I know I'm going to die.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
